name: "Live Like Kings"
description:
"Live Like Kings"

This design is one of our first tees printed and has had HUGE success already! 

Like our other tees, this design is printed on to an organic t-shirt, made from 70% Bamboo/30% Organic Cotton! 

We are one of the only clothing companies that try to help the world in every which way possible, so even our chosen print methods are friendlier than the norm. Our printers are 1 of only 4 companies in the U.K that use an innovative new ink that is NON SOLVENT BASED! This means less nasties to hurt the world we live in!

Our Tees are super comfy, Eco friendly and hopefully you'll love the designs!
So show your love and rep. a huckleberry clothing T-shirt!
